column2:
"Yo <%me>!
You seem to be doing fine in ARKS."
"I heard a lot of good things about you."
"I know that you are capable, but you should take a break too."
"Ah, Io! Hey, over here!"
"Io! It's been a while! How are you doing?"
"It's been a while. Although in my case, I've been seeing you around."
"Other than your Live concerts, that broadcast half a year ago too."
"Ahh,<%me> was in trouble then. Feels kinda nostalgic recalling it."
"Senpai and Quna know each other huh."
"<%me>, are you not surprised that I am acquainted with Io?"
"I worked together with Afin and Io in an ARKS project before."
"It was really tough that time."
"Ugh... I am sorry for that..."
"It's fine. It was a good memory for me."
"More importantly Io, you haven't changed your appearance eh."
"Quna... Not that topic again."
"Hey, <%me>. What do you think?"
"1. Agreed."
"2. I think it's fine."
"Senpai too! Man, give me a break."
"Hmm, I see. That was Afin's opinion as well."
"Man, give me a break. Why are the two of you talking about me."
"Io has the potential, it would be a waste to not use it."
"I'll do a makeover for you from your head to toe okay? Perhaps you could be an idol too! Wanna give it a try?"
"Q-Quit joking around! I definitely don't wish to be an idol."
"Ahh, she left. I didn't mean to be rude..."
"Seeing people smiling and dancing to their favorite songs that I sing, isn't a bad feeling."
